Title: Equivalence between Zwanziger's horizon function and Gribov's no-pole  ghost form factor
Authors: A. J. Gomez and M. S. Guimaraes and R. F. Sobreiro and S. P. Sorella
Abstract: The ghost form factor entering the Gribov no-pole condition is evaluated till the third order in the gauge fields. The resulting expression turns out to coincide with Zwanziger's horizon function implementing the restriction to the Gribov region in the functional integral.
